snippet.title: Paris Bennett Admits He Murdered His Sister to Punish His Mother | Psychopath with Piers Morgan
snippet.description:
Piers Morgan ventures behind bars for an extraordinary encounter with diagnosed psychopath Paris Bennett, a man who is more intelligent, more cunning and more manipulative than any criminal Piers has met before. Catch up now on the ITV Hub: https://bit.ly/322PihF
